# ─── Logs / debug dumps ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Anchor `logs/` and `debug/` to the repo root so the patterns don't
# case-insensitively swallow `client/src/screens/Logs/` on macOS/Windows
# filesystems — that happened once and left a real source file
# un-tracked until CI noticed on a clean checkout.
*.log
/logs/
/debug/
*.dmp
crash-*.txt

